            <title>[CAMEL-16378] Camel MDC - Not propagating custom keys when using Split with Parallel Processing</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-16378</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When using&#160;MDC in Camel (with&#160;custom mdc keys configured) values are not being&#160;propagate when using Split with parallel processing.&lt;/p&gt;

